08:57.954 --> 09:03.042
I just thought that's what, you know,
girls like to hear after...

09:03.751 --> 09:04.752
you know.

09:08.339 --> 09:10.341
You're such an asshole.
Do you know that?

09:12.218 --> 09:13.719
-Just go home.
-Wait, Casey.

09:13.803 --> 09:15.221
