09:39.704 --> 09:43.708
[Sam]  When it snows, it gets really quiet
because snow actually absorbs sound.

09:44.500 --> 09:46.460
-Can I have some blankets?
-No.

09:47.628 --> 09:49.046
So when you get a snowstorm,

09:49.130 --> 09:51.716
it's like soundproofing
for the entire planet.

09:55.094 --> 09:59.599
Sometimes I wish it would snow
and just never stop snowing.

10:17.992 --> 10:19.660
[muffled rock music playing]

10:19.744 --> 10:21.746
-[chattering]
-[laughing]

10:28.294 --> 10:31.631
